Attribution & license retention
-------------------------------
The overlay deliberately does NOT touch the upstream `LICENSE` file, any
`NOTICE` files, `README` attribution, or the `website/` docs of a Hermes
install. Branding is applied only to customer-visible product strings and via
Hermes's native skin engine. The MIT copyright and permission notice above are
retained in every Hermes install this overlay is applied to, as the license
requires. Attribution stays; only the customer-facing brand changes.

The JARVIS name, banner art, persona, and overlay tooling in this repository
are the property of their respective owner and are not part of the upstream
MIT-licensed project.
